;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\" data-sourcepos=\"19:1-19:157\">Keesokan harinya, Kancil kembali berulah. Ia melihat seekor <strong style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:inline;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 0px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\">kelinci</strong> sedang asyik menggali tanah mencari umbi-umbian. Kancil mendekat dengan senyum lebar.</p><p style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-weight:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 16px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\" data-sourcepos=\"21:1-21:159\">\"Kelinci, maukah kau membantuku?\" tanya Kancil dengan suara lembut. \"Aku menemukan ladang wortel yang sangat banyak, tapi aku tidak bisa mengambilnya sendiri.\"</p><p style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-weight:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 16px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\" data-sourcepos=\"23:1-23:73\">Kelinci yang polos langsung bersemangat. \"Benarkah, Kancil? Di mana itu?\"</p><p style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-weight:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 16px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\" data-sourcepos=\"25:1-25:168\">\"Ikutlah aku,\" kata Kancil sambil menuntun Kelinci ke tepi jurang. \"Wortel-wortel itu ada di bawah sana. Kau saja yang mengambilnya, nanti aku akan menunggumu di sini.\"</p><p style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-weight:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 16px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\" data-sourcepos=\"27:1-27:215\">Kelinci yang tidak curiga langsung melompat ke bawah jurang. Begitu Kelinci sudah di bawah, Kancil langsung berbalik dan pergi meninggalkannya sendirian. Kelinci pun kebingungan dan kesulitan keluar dari jurang itu.</p><hr style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-weight:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 8px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\" data-sourcepos=\"29:1-29:3\"><p style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-weight:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 16px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\" data-sourcepos=\"31:1-31:183\">Semakin hari, semakin banyak hewan yang jengkel dengan kenakalan Kancil. Mereka mulai menghindari Kancil. Kancil jadi kesepian dan tidak punya teman bermain. Ia mulai merasa menyesal.</p><p style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-weight:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 16px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\" data-sourcepos=\"33:1-33:200\">Suatu sore, Kancil melihat seekor <strong style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:inline;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 0px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\">gajah</strong> tua sedang kesulitan mengangkat batang pohon yang jatuh. Kancil ingin membantu, tapi ia ragu. Ia takut Gajah akan menolaknya karena kenakalannya selama ini.</p><p style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-weight:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 16px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\" data-sourcepos=\"35:1-35:104\">Namun, rasa kasihan Kancil lebih besar. Ia memberanikan diri mendekat. \"Gajah, bolehkah aku membantumu?\"</p><p style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-weight:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 16px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\" data-sourcepos=\"37:1-37:91\">Gajah menatap Kancil dengan heran. \"Kau mau membantuku, Kancil? Setelah semua kenakalanmu?\"</p><p style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-weight:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 16px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\" data-sourcepos=\"39:1-39:102\">Kancil menunduk. \"Aku tahu aku salah, Gajah. Aku sangat menyesal. Aku berjanji tidak akan nakal lagi.\"</p><p style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-weight:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 16px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\" data-sourcepos=\"41:1-41:57\">Gajah tersenyum tipis. \"Baiklah, Kancil. Mari kita coba.\"</p><p style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-weight:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 16px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\" data-sourcepos=\"43:1-43:297\">Dengan bantuan Kancil yang cerdik, batang pohon itu akhirnya bisa disingkirkan. Gajah berterima kasih kepada Kancil. Sejak saat itu, Kancil benar-benar berubah. Ia tidak lagi menjahili hewan lain, bahkan sering membantu mereka. Kancil pun akhirnya memiliki banyak teman dan hidup bahagia di hutan.</p><hr style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-weight:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 8px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\" data-sourcepos=\"45:1-45:3\"><p style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-weight:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.1