mal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:inline;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 0px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\">lomba mewarnai tingkat Kabupaten Lamongan</strong> yang diselenggarakan di Gedung Olahraga (GOR) Lamongan. Ajang ini menjadi wadah bagi anak-anak untuk menunjukkan kreativitas dan bakat seni mereka di hadapan juri dan peserta dari berbagai TK di seluruh Lamongan.</p><p style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-weight:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 16px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\" data-sourcepos=\"9:1-9:362\">Sebanyak puluhan anak dari TK Dharma Wanita Lamongan tampak antusias membawa perlengkapan mewarnai masing-masing. Dengan krayon, pensil warna, dan spidol di tangan, mereka siap menuangkan imajinasi ke atas lembar gambar. Tema lomba tahun ini berfokus pada <strong style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:inline;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 0px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\">kekayaan budaya dan alam Lamongan</strong>, seperti gambar ikan bandeng, perahu, atau pemandangan khas pesisir.</p><p style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-weight:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 16px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\" data-sourcepos=\"11:1-11:424\">\"Kami sangat bangga melihat semangat anak-anak hari ini,\" ujar Ibu [Nama Kepala Sekolah/Guru], Kepala TK Dharma Wanita Lamongan. \"Lomba ini bukan hanya tentang menang atau kalah, tetapi lebih kepada memberikan pengalaman berharga bagi mereka untuk <strong style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:inline;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 0px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\">mengembangkan kreativitas, melatih fokus, dan membangun rasa percaya diri</strong>. Kami juga ingin memperkenalkan dan menanamkan cinta terhadap kearifan lokal Lamongan sejak dini.\"</p><p style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-weight:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 16px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\" data-sourcepos=\"13:1-13:329\">Selama lomba berlangsung, anak-anak terlihat serius namun tetap menikmati setiap goresan warna. Beberapa di antaranya bahkan terlihat berdiskusi kecil dengan temannya tentang pilihan warna yang tepat. Para guru pendamping dan orang tua yang hadir memberikan dukungan penuh, sesekali memberikan semangat kepada putra-putri mereka.</p><p style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-weight:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 16px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\" data-sourcepos=\"15:1-15:442\">Partisipasi dalam lomba mewarnai ini merupakan bagian dari upaya TK Dharma Wanita Lamongan untuk <strong style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:inline;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-se