reng, sayur bening, dan buah pisang</strong>], yang disiapkan dengan standar kebersihan tinggi.</p><p style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-weight:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 16px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\" data-sourcepos=\"11:1-11:374\">Ibu <strong style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:inline;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 0px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\">Kepala Sekolah</strong>, Kepala TK Dharma Wanita Lamong, menyatakan, \"Kami sangat bersyukur dapat melaksanakan program makan siang gratis ini. Kami percaya bahwa asupan gizi yang baik sangat fundamental bagi perkembangan kognitif dan fisik anak-anak. Dengan perut kenyang dan gizi terpenuhi, mereka bisa lebih fokus belajar, bermain, dan berinteraksi di sekolah.\"</p><p style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-weight:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 16px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\" data-sourcepos=\"13:1-13:372\">Lebih lanjut, <strong>Kepala sekolah</strong> menambahkan bahwa program ini juga memiliki dampak positif dalam mengajarkan anak-anak tentang <strong style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:inline;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 0px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\">pentingnya kebersamaan dan etika makan</strong>. Sebelum menyantap hidangan, anak-anak diajarkan untuk mencuci tangan, berdoa, dan makan dengan tertib. Mereka juga didorong untuk menghabiskan makanan dan belajar berbagi dengan teman.</p><p style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-weight:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 16px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\" data-sourcepos=\"15:1-15:280\">Pemandangan saat makan siang begitu mengharukan. Anak-anak yang biasanya aktif berlarian, kini duduk manis di meja makan, saling berbagi cerita sambil menikmati hidangan. Tawa riang dan celotehan polos mereka mengisi ruang makan, menciptakan ikatan persahabatan yang semakin erat.</p><p style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-weight:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 16px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\" data-sourcepos=\"17:1-17:345\">Orang tua siswa pun menyambut baik program ini. Salah satu wali murid, Ibu<strong style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:inline;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;gap:normal;hyphens:manual;inset:auto;interactivity:auto;isolation:auto;line-height:1.15 !important;margin:0px !important 0px 0px;marker:none;mask:none;offset:normal;opacity:1;order:0;orphans:2;outline:rgb(27, 28, 29) none 0px;overlay:none;padding:0px;page:auto;perspective:none;position:static;quotes:auto;r:0px;resize:none;rotate:none;rx:auto;ry:auto;scale:none;speak:normal;stroke:none;transform:none;transition:all;translate:none;visibility:visible;widows:2;x:0px;y:0px;zoom:1;\"> Fitri</strong>, mengungkapkan, \"Program ini sangat membantu kami, terutama bagi orang tua yang sibuk. Kami tidak perlu khawatir lagi tentang bekal anak, dan yang terpenting, kami tahu anak kami mendapatkan makanan yang bergizi dan sehat di sekolah.\"</p><p style=\"animation:0s ease 0s 1 normal none running none;appearance:none;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border:0px none rgb(27, 28, 29);clear:none;clip:auto;color:rgb(27, 28, 29);columns:auto;contain:none;container:none;content:normal;cursor:auto;cx:0px;cy:0px;d:none;direction:ltr;display:block;fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);filter:none;flex:0 1 auto;float:none;font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-feature-settings:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size-adjust:none;font-size:16px;font-stretch:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-variation-setti